**CAREER SUMMARY**
I have extensive experience in HTML, CSS, JQuery , JavaScript , PHP , MySQL and Software projects analysis and have designed and developed various websites and web applications for companies and organizations. I'm also working as a webmaster. My domain of expertise is the development of web applications with strong back-end supported by an attractive and innovative front-end. I'm also well versed with open source technologies and frameworks like Joomla, OpenCart and Wordpress. Also i am working in training field about web design and web development
